nodes.name: D-glyceraldehyde-3-phosphate:NAD+ oxidoreductase (phosphorylating)
nodes.rxn: D-Glyceraldehyde 3-phosphate + Orthophosphate + NAD+ <=> 3-Phospho-D-glyceroyl phosphate + NADH + H+

nodes.name: L-Aspartic acid:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Aspartate + H2O + Oxygen <=> Oxaloacetate + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: L-glutamate:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Glutamate + NAD+ + H2O <=> 2-Oxoglutarate + Ammonia + NADH + H+

nodes.name: L-Glutamate:ammonia ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + L-Glutamate + Ammonia <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + L-Glutamine

nodes.name: acetyl-CoA:oxaloacetate C-acetyltransferase [(pro-S)-carboxymethyl-forming, ADP-phosphorylating]
nodes.rxn: ATP + Citrate + CoA <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + Acetyl-CoA + Oxaloacetate

nodes.name: Pyruvate:carbon-dioxide ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Pyruvate + HCO3- <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + Oxaloacetate

nodes.name: 2-oxoglutarate:ferredoxin oxidoreductase (decarboxylating)
nodes.rxn: 2 Reduced ferredoxin + Succinyl-CoA + CO2 + 2 H+ <=> 2 Oxidized ferredoxin + 2-Oxoglutarate + CoA

nodes.name: pyruvate:ferredoxin 2-oxidoreductase (CoA-acetylating)
nodes.rxn: 2 Reduced ferredoxin + Acetyl-CoA + CO2 + 2 H+ <=> 2 Oxidized ferredoxin + Pyruvate + CoA
